PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FWatch Nick Smith's report in full - A
OL,8,Fwarning that some may find this video
OL,9,Freport and the content in this article
OL,10,Fdistressing
OL,12,FITV News has obtained exclusive
OL,13,Ffootage from the animal welfare
OL,14,Forganisation, Protect the Wild, who
OL,15,Fsecretly filmed at farms breeding and
OL,16,Fsupplying birds for organised shoots
OL,17,Facross the UK.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FIn total, seven UK farms were
OL,8,Finvestigated. One member of Protect
OL,9,FThe Wild worked undercover at Heart of
OL,10,FEngland Farms Ltd in Warwickshire for
OL,11,Fseveral weeks at during last year's
OL,12,Fbreeding season.
OL,14,FHis footage allegedly shows several
OL,15,Fbreaches of the DEFRA Code of Conduct
OL,16,Fon animal welfare and potential
OL,17,Fenvironmental hazards.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FHe claims birds were often kept in in
OL,8,Fsmall, overcrowded cages with little
OL,9,For no enrichment, and were denied
OL,10,Fveterinary care and were routinely
OL,11,Ffitted with beak management devices to
OL,12,Finhibit their natural behaviours.
OL,14,FThe worker alleged that a hen was made
OL,15,Fto continue laying eggs despite having
OL,16,Fa damaged leg, and a member of the
OL,17,Ffarm's management even appeared to
OL,18,Fadmit to the improper use of rodent
OL,19,Fpoisons by laying them in the grass
OL,20,Funder outdoor bird cages to prevent
OL,21,Frats eating bird eggs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FThis practice is banned under
OL,8,Fenvironmental law due to concerns that
OL,9,Fit can seriously harm wild bird
OL,10,Fpopulations.
OL,12,FAn undercover worker said: "I saw
OL,13,Fshocking things. A bird had a damaged
OL,14,Fleg and when this was brought to the
OL,15,Fattention of one of the workers, he
OL,16,Fliterally just said, 'well, you know,
OL,17,Fas long as she can still lay an egg,
OL,18,Fdon't worry about it.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,F"It's literally a case of breeding as
OL,8,Fmany birds as possible to survive for
OL,9,Fas long as possible to be sold and
OL,10,Fthen shot."
OL,12,FIn other parts of the footage, a farm
OL,13,Fworker is seen removing beak
OL,14,Fmanagement devices from dead birds
OL,15,Fsaying they "get stuck under the
OL,16,Ffeeders and just don't eat, they get
OL,17,Fstuck and just die", with more shots
OL,18,Fof bins full of dead pheasant hens.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FThe undercover worker claims no
OL,8,Frecords were kept of the number of
OL,9,Fbirds that died on the farm.
OL,11,FIn other sections of footage, to
OL,12,Fprevent fighting, male birds are seen
OL,13,Fplaced alone in small cages with
OL,14,Flittle room to move.
OL,16,FA dead pheasant hen was found with
OL,17,Fholes through it's septum, the
OL,18,Fpiercing of which is illegal under
OL,19,Fcurrent animal welfare laws.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FRobert Pownall, Founder of Protect The
OL,8,FWild, said: "We have conducted what we
OL,9,Fbelieve to be the largest undercover
OL,10,Finvestigation into the British bird
OL,11,Fshooting industry. You've got probably
OL,12,Fhundreds, if not thousands of these
OL,13,Fcages in fields across England, where
OL,14,Fthese birds are not able to show any
OL,15,Fnatural behaviours.
OL,17,F"There isn't proper legislation, isn't
OL,18,Fproper regulation, there isn't proper
OL,19,Foversight of what they're doing or how
OL,20,Fthey're doing it, and that is a
OL,21,Fserious, serious problem."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FShooting as an industry is estimated
OL,8,Fto be worth around #3 billion each
OL,9,Fyear to the UK economy (according to
OL,10,Ffigures compiled by the British
OL,11,FAssociation for Shooting and
OL,12,FConservation) and it relies on a
OL,13,Fconstant supply of birds.
OL,15,FDEFRA-sourced figures estimate that
OL,16,Fbetween 40 and 60 million pheasants
OL,17,Fand partridges are bred or imported
OL,18,Ffrom farms to be released into the
OL,19,Fcountryside during the summer months
OL,20,Ffor shooting parties to hunt during
OL,21,Fthe winter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FHowever, figures from the Game and
OL,8,FWildlife Conservation Trust suggests
OL,9,Fonly 37% are shot. 25% die before the
OL,10,Fshooting season even begins, often
OL,11,Featen by foxes or killed on roads. On
OL,12,Faverage, just 16% actually survive the
OL,13,Fwinter shooting season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FThose representing the shooting
OL,8,Findustry claim they go to great
OL,9,Flengths to maintain the countryside
OL,10,Fand wild habitats, while many animal
OL,11,Fwelfare groups say that releasing such
OL,12,Fa high number of non-native birds puts
OL,13,Fhuge pressure on ecosystems and harms
OL,14,Fother species.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FThe footage was also presented to
OL,8,FAyesha Smart, a specialist barrister
OL,9,Fin animal welfare law, who reviewed it
OL,10,Ffor Protect The Wild, she says: "These
OL,11,Fgame bird farms, they are less
OL,12,Ffrequently visited in comparison to,
OL,13,Fsay, for example, your factory farms
OL,14,Fwhere you've got pigs and cows and
OL,15,Fchickens.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,F"So there's no compulsory requirement
OL,8,Fto go in and inspect them. In terms of
OL,9,Fthe environment conditions these
OL,10,Fanimals are put in, they're put in
OL,11,Fcramped, barren cages. It's
OL,12,Feffectively like being in solitary
OL,13,Fconfinement in a prison, they're
OL,14,Fresorting to aggression with other
OL,15,Fbirds because they're so hemmed in.
OL,17,F"When you compare it to the
OL,18,Flegislation, there's no underlying
OL,19,Fjustification for that."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FThe Game Farmer's Association, an
OL,8,Findustry body representing many of the
OL,9,FUK's game bird farms said: "The GFA
OL,10,Fpromotes high welfare standards and
OL,11,Fbest practice across the game farming
OL,12,Fsector and the overwhelming majority
OL,13,Fof game farms operate to these high
OL,14,Fstandards.
OL,16,F"Where issues arise, we work with
OL,17,Fmembers to address them and improve
OL,18,Fpractice. However, the GFA does not
OL,19,Fhave legal powers of enforcement."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,FWe reached out to Heart of England
OL,8,FFarms Ltd with multiple requests to
OL,9,Faddress the allegations, but they have
OL,10,Fnot yet provided a response.
OL,12,FWe also approached the Department for
OL,13,FFood, Environment and Rural Affairs
OL,14,F(DEFRA) and the Animal and Plant
OL,15,FHealth Agency (APHA) for comment.
OL,17,FA DEFRA spokesperson said: "We want to
OL,18,Fsee the highest possible animal
OL,19,Fwelfare and environmental standards
OL,20,Facross the gamebird industry.
OL,26,@yD@\OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778163069
OL,3,C'Cramped cages & unnecessary
OL,4,Csuffering': Undercover inside a game
OL,5,Cbird farm
OL,7,F"In March, we announced that we would
OL,8,Freview the evidence and issues
OL,9,Fassociated with recreational gamebird
OL,10,Fshooting and release."
OL,12,FAn APHA spokesperson said: "We take
OL,13,Fbreaches of animal welfare legislation
OL,14,Fvery seriously and investigate every
OL,15,Fallegation that is reported to us.
OL,17,F"We will always take appropriate
OL,18,Faction where non-compliances with
OL,19,Fwelfare regulations are found."
OL,26,@rD@VO]tD@\OUyD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/16
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
